        "Title": "ChEMBL Molecular Sampler",
        "Description": "A simple sampler of the ChEMBL database using their API. It looks for similar molecules to the input molecule and returns a list of 100 molecules by default. This model has been developed by Ersilia. It posts queries to an online server.",
